# PrimeVue LLMs Documentation Reference

This project uses PrimeVue v4. When working with PrimeVue components, use the official LLM-optimized documentation.

## Documentation Endpoints

| Endpoint                                | Description                                       |
| --------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------- |
| https://primevue.org/llms/llms.txt      | Structured list of key documentation pages        |
| https://primevue.org/llms/llms-full.txt | Complete list of all PrimeVue documentation pages |
| https://primevue.org/{component}.md     | Markdown documentation for specific component     |

